678
0:53:37,694 --> 0:53:39,129
Excellencies.


679
0:53:39,129 --> 0:53:43,1
The Archduke Ferdinand of Ruthenia
has decided to visit this establishment.


680
0:53:43,1 --> 0:53:44,635
It is an honor, Excellency.


681
0:53:44,635 --> 0:53:46,537
His Highness wants
some relaxation.


682
0:53:46,537 --> 0:53:49,206
We were against it,
after this morning's incident.


683
0:53:49,206 --> 0:53:51,575
You must see that everything
is in order.


684
0:53:51,575 --> 0:53:54,444
Of course. This is a most
respectable establishment.


685
0:53:54,444 --> 0:54:9,259
I hope not. I told you,
he wanted some relaxation.


686
0:54:9,259 --> 0:54:16,733
Now, leave it to me and get out!


687
0:54:16,733 --> 0:54:20,404
Lift up your glass on high


688
