698
0:54:50,534 --> 0:54:54,204
And a pledge that's warm and gay


699
0:54:54,204 --> 0:54:57,908
"I promise to
Remember you


700
0:54:57,908 --> 0:55:0,444
"The way you are today"


701
0:55:0,444 --> 0:55:2,846
- The Blutwurst.
- Here we are, mein Herr,


702
0:55:2,846 --> 0:55:7,918
the riesen Blutwurst,
the greatest delicacy in all Vienna.


703
0:55:7,918 --> 0:55:12,723
The pigs for the Blutwurst are bred
here in our Vienna woods.


704
0:55:12,723 --> 0:55:16,93
They were slaughtered
only this morning.


705
0:55:16,93 --> 0:55:20,797
The blood must be quite fresh.
Yes, yes.


706
0:55:20,797 --> 0:55:23,266
In Vienna we have the best
of everything.


707
0:55:23,266 --> 0:55:24,868
Enjoy yourselves.


708
0:55:24,868 --> 0:55:29,94
And drink it down, down
Down, down, down


709
0:55:29,94 --> 0:55:34,711
Down, down, down
Down, down


710
0:55:34,711 --> 0:55:38,81
Lift up your glass on high


711
0:55:38,81 --> 0:55:40,617
Drink to the days
