712
0:55:40,617 --> 0:55:42,52
Waiter!


713
0:55:42,52 --> 0:55:44,688
Some day we'll meet again


714
0:55:44,688 --> 0:55:48,892
Remember me till then


715
0:55:48,892 --> 0:55:52,396
Lift up your glass on high


716
0:55:52,396 --> 0:55:56,5
A sausage! But what did I say?
This is indeed a place of fun!


717
